"Your Account Has been Logged in. We Would Like to Inform you With this Message that if you Have Not Logged in During this Time, your Data May be at Risk. We Recommend that you Change your Password Immediately or Contact us. We Care about the Security of your Data.\n"
"\n"
"%(domain)s%(language)s/profile/%(username)s?password-reset=true\n"
"\n"
