"\n"
"%(domain)s%(language)s?verification-code=%(verification_code)s&id=%(id)s\n"
"\n"
"This Link is Valid for the Next 24 hours. After this Time, you Will Need to Register Again for Security Reasons. If you Did Not Register, Please Ignore this E-mail.\n"
"Wesiq Team."

