"target=\"_blank\">tento</a> odkaz potvrdíte svoj e-mail a budete automaticky"
" prihlásený do svojho nového účtu. Tento odkaz je platný nasledujúcich 24 "
"hodín. Po uplynutí tohto času bude z bezpečnostných dôvodov potrebné "
"registráciu zopakovať."
msgstr ""
"Thank You for your Registration. To Complete the Registration Process and "
"Activate your Account, you Must Verify your E-mail Address. Click on <a "
"href=\"%(domain)s%(language)s?verification-"
"code=%(verification_code)s&id=%(id)s\" title=\"Complete Registration\" "
"target=\"_blank\">This</a> to Confirm your E-mail and you Will be "
"Automatically Logged Into your New Account. This Link is Valid for the Next "
"24 hours. After this Time, you Will Need to Register Again for Security "
"Reasons."

